                  </hi>. I live at Stockbridge-terrace, and am a coach-maker—on the 11th of June I was at work at Mr. Miller's, Westbourne-street, Pimlico—I left a saw, a hammer, and screw-driver there, and the next morning they were gone—this is my saw.</p>
